title: Ireland Car Registrations
description: Car Registrations in Ireland decreased to 4527 in October from 7315 in September of 2022. Car Registrations in Ireland averaged 7912.93  from 1965 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 32961  in January of 2008 and a record low of 474  in December of 2009. This page provides - Ireland Car Registrations - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Statistics Office Ireland
